  • Method Details

    • exportData

      boolean exportData(List<Lecture> lectures, String path) throws IOException
      Exports schedule data to an external file.
      Parameters:
      lectures - List of lectures whose data will be saved.
      path - The path where the exported data will be saved.
      Returns:
      true if the export is successful, false otherwise.
      Throws:
      IOException - If an I/O error occurs during the export process.
